            </div>
</div>
</header>

<main class="flex-grow w-full flex flex-col items-center py-8 md:py-12 px-4 md:px-6">
<div class="w-full max-w-[800px] flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-12">

<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
<div class="flex justify-between items-end">
<p class="text-[#9c8749] dark:text-[#d4c59a] text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Etapa 2 de 5</p>
<span class="text-[#1c180d] dark:text-white text-sm font-medium">40% Completo</span>
</div>
<div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-[#e8e2ce] dark:bg-[#443c24] rounded-full overflow-hidden">
<div class="h-full bg-primary rounded-full transition-all duration-500 ease-out" style="width: 40%;"></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="text-center space-y-3">
<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1c180d] dark:text-white tracking-tight leading-tight">
                    Motivação e Perfil
                </h1>
<p class="text-[#9c8749] dark:text-[#d4c59a] text-base md:text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                    Queremos entender seus objetivos e desafios para personalizar sua jornada de aprendizado.
                </p>
</div>

