<span class="text-sm text-[#9c8749] dark:text-[#b0a070] mt-1 leading-snug">Preocupação com o retorno do investimento a curto prazo.</span>
</div>
</div>
</label>

<label class="cursor-pointer group relative">
<input class="peer sr-only" name="fear" type="radio" value="time"/>
<div class="p-5 rounded-lg border border-[#e8e2ce] dark:border-[#554b2f] bg-background-light dark:bg-[#221e10] hover:border-primary/50 transition-all h-full flex items-start gap-4">
<div class="radio-circle mt-1 size-5 rounded-full border-2 border-[#d1c8b0] dark:border-[#665c40] flex-shrink-0 transition-colors"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<span class="font-semibold text-[#1c180d] dark:text-white">Disponibilidade de Tempo</span>
<span class="text-sm text-[#9c8749] dark:text-[#b0a070] mt-1 leading-snug">Dificuldade em conciliar estudos com a agenda profissional.</span>
</div>
</div>
</label>

<label class="cursor-pointer group relative">
